des:
FATE FM UK the go-to station for Essex,
Kent and surrounding areas of London catering to you, the dedicated listener. 

Let our family of DJ’s spin your favourite tracks from across the globe throughout the week.

Whether you need something great to listen to on your way to or from work, or pottering around the house, FATE FM UK provides you with hours of entertainment and great music including hosting of events across Essex so don't forget to check in on our EVENTS page for all the latest!
